  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_998F1DA0-0832-0135-A692-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Account Navigation, click the <strong>Settings </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_feature_options_tab" data-step-uuid="f65bc1a9-0db3-4461-925d-1cd564780e33">
    <h2 id="open_feature_options_tab" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Feature Options Tab</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/976/434/original/8b0d8e21-32ba-41b4-95dd-896c347684b1.png" srcset="" alt="Open Feature Options Tab" height="109" width="782">
