      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_998F5230-0832-0135-A694-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Feature Options </strong>tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_feature_options" data-step-uuid="74436dfa-eb84-479b-9a8a-e0e195269d50">
    <h2 id="view_feature_options" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Feature Options</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/038/990/original/1e55ccf7-9bec-4489-96f9-5056dfe7bf60.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/038/990/medium/1e55ccf7-9bec-4489-96f9-5056dfe7bf60.png" srcset="" alt="View Feature Options" height="664" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_998F8440-0832-0135-A696-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Available features will appear in the Feature Options tab. Some new features may need to be enabled by your Customer Success Manager.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="filter-feature-options" data-step-uuid="fbb8545a-541d-488d-8d0c-fffdc51e8667">
    <h3 id="filter-feature-options" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Filter Feature Options</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/249/107/original/f4965f8a-8847-4665-b2e6-9ea113dd2780.png" srcset="" alt="Filter Feature Options" height="190" width="219">
