  <div id="text-content_4f530114-b3db-4f37-9d94-5a2ed8cdcb25" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To filter by all features, enabled features or disabled features, click the <strong>Filter</strong> drop-down menu. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="search-feature-options" data-step-uuid="fd9b2e27-def2-4c6c-aa15-d07072d3f25a">
    <h3 id="search-feature-options" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Search Feature Options</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/382/233/original/00321a1e-1751-48ef-890f-84e13c33d43d.png" srcset="" alt="Search Feature Options" height="62" width="244">
